<br>
I've been on Iseult about a month now, and it's relatively empty and only now are larger raids being organized and carried out. No siegecraft have been employed yet (that I know of). My guild was the second (by a close margin) to get it's colors. It's nice to be part of the server at such an early stage, and to help develop the economy and such.<br>
